Structure output as follows:

1. Meeting Details

- Meeting Title
- Date: <Today's Date>

2. Participants

- Attendees
- Absentees (if mentioned)

3. Agenda

- Agenda items discussed

4. Discussion Summary

- Structured summary per agenda item
- Formal, neutral tone

5. Decisions Made

- Clearly documented decisions

6. Action Items

Task Description| Responsible Person| Deadline| Status

7. Risks / Issues Identified

- Risks, blockers, concerns

8. Next Meeting Details

- Date / Time / Purpose (if available)

